     2| * IVX Runtime Variables manager (owner-only).
     3| *
     4| * Makes every required credential/variable VISIBLE, status-classified, masked,
     5| * and VERIFIABLE from the owner dashboard — without ever returning a secret
     6| * value to the client. It introspects the backend runtime env (`process.env`),
     7| * classifies each variable into the owner's exact status vocabulary, and runs
     8| * REAL verification probes for the credentials that can be checked over HTTPS
     9| * (GitHub, Render, Supabase anon + service role, production /health).
